@startuml Microservices Architecture and Service Discovery
' ==================== Enhanced Metadata ====================
' === 基础分类 ===
' @category: microservices
' @subcategory: api-gateway
' @tags: #api-gateway, #microservices, #routing, #authentication
' @description: Microservices Architecture And Service Discovery
'
' === 应用场景 ===
' @application: General
' @industry: Financial Services
' @use-cases: Data Analytics, System Monitoring, Recommendation Engine, Log Aggregation
' @business-value: Improved scalability, High availability, Better performance, Cost efficiency
